Facebook Plans ‘Dislike’ Button Facebook Inc. is going beyond the “like” button, CEO Mark Zuckerberg said.
The social network is working on something akin to a “dislike” button, he said during a wide-ranging Q&A on Tuesday at Facebook’s headquarters that was streamed online.
